ğŸ§  How CTOR Bots Work
A bot is a JavaScript function that receives:

the current board

the botâ€™s color ("R" or "B")

the move history

optional helper functions

It must return a move:

js
{ row: Number, col: Number }
ğŸŸ¦ Minimal bot example
js
