ğŸ“˜ Bot API Specification
Your bot receives:

Parameter	Type	Description
board	string[8][8]	8Ã—8 matrix containing "R", "B", or "."
color	"R" or "B"	Your botâ€™s color
history	Array	List of previous moves
helpers	Object	Optional helper functions
Your bot must return:

js
{ row: Number, col: Number }
If the bot returns an illegal move â†’ it loses automatically.

ğŸ§© Example: A Greedy Bot
js
export function greedyBot(board, color) {
  let best = null;
  let bestScore = -1;

  for (let r = 0; r < 8; r++) {
    for (let c = 0; c < 8; c++) {
      if (board[r][c] !== ".") continue;

      const score = evaluateMove(board, r, c, color);
      if (score > bestScore) {
        bestScore = score;
        best = { row: r, col: c };
      }
    }
  }

  return best || null;
}
